{"tid":298481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪五日四夜行請求評","createTime":"2017-06-26T10:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T10:33:15.000Z","uid":96677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec9ab54d0e0fb9c1e028c63769de94e2acba8a8b","tid":298481,"uid":96677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:22:49.000Z","msg":"Day 1:<br />\n<br />\nArrive at airport (KIX) -- 京都 -- 伏見稻荷 &gt; 袛園四條 &gt;花見小路&gt;八坂神社&gt;二三年坂&gt;清水寺<br />\n<br />\n Day 2: 京都-JR「龜岡」站徒歩約8分鍾--保津川遊船-- 下船處步行15分鐘到嵯峨嵐山站&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n嵐山--嵯峨野竹林, 野宮神社, 嵐山渡月橋 --離開京都 --大阪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n Day 3: 黑門市場 --梅田 -- 道頓堀 -- 心齋橋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 4: Universal Studio<br />\n<br />\nDay 5: 大阪城 -- Airport<br />\n<br />\n其實未計機票 不過如果第一日行程可以減少啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係同家人去咖 shopping冇咩興趣 所謂揀左去海遊館 巴打點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfc37b8c0569552b4b4304616475d8bc14b4fdd","tid":298481,"uid":23751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"唔買野你個day3會好悶"},{"pid":"fdb360d2166f866a38b69bd8350f548383a7a1ad","tid":298481,"uid":96677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔買野你個day3會好悶</blockquote><br />\n唔小心未改番梅田去海遊館添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁巴打有咩推介大阪景點"},{"pid":"67855784f838a4bba9e5f434613d894f4f050413","tid":298481,"uid":96677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4906ad90e1ed137dee3f929bbd959d0052be92","tid":298481,"uid":96677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a63ae2337e8035c488e106d3da98f4ea5aca70","tid":298481,"uid":61788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:33:15.000Z","msg":"我去過大阪生活今昔館，感覺幾好<br />\n你上網睇下資料～<br />\n我見好多人去大阪都唔會plan去呢度咁（唔肯定）"}]}